replies.txt_content:
summon 雪球 x y z {Motion:[方向]}
关于运动方向看这个贴，第二个隐藏内容里
http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-425160-1-1.html

举例：
朝东射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[10.0,0.0,0.0]}
朝西射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[-10.0,0.0,0.0]}
朝上射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[0.0,10.0,0.0]}
朝下射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[0.0,-10.0,0.0]}
朝北射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[0.0,0.0,-10.0]}
朝南射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[0.0,0.0,10.0]}
朝东南上射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[10.0,10.0,10.0]}
朝西北下射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[-10.0,-10.0,-10.0]}
朝西南射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[-10.0,0.0,10.0]}
朝东北射：/summon Snowball x y z {Motion:[10.0,-10.0,-10.0]}
数值最大10.0，最小-10.0
